item.title: Meaning of Life by Zentara
item.description: http://zentara.net/ => Deep Thoughts => Want to know the meaning of life? This is the essence of the meaning of life Once you read it, you will never be able to get it out of your subconcious mind. It will crack open the door to the next level of conciousness. .................................................................... Your most previous incarnation, was a 9-month life inside your mother. During this life, you were developing the organs needed to exist on the next level.
